docs.abstract: To the founding fathers, foreign influence on an American president was an abiding fear and a basis for impeachment.

docs.lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Alexander Hamilton, as usual, got right to the heart of the matter. docs.abstract: Gordon D. Sondland, the United States ambassador to the European Union set to testify in a public hearing Wednesday, has a lot of explaining to do.
docs.snippet: Gordon D. Sondland, the United States ambassador to the European Union set to testify in a public hearing Wednesday, has a lot of explaining to do.
docs.lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Gordon D. Sondland, the American ambassador to the European Union, has emerged as a critical witness in the impeachment inquiry into President Trump’s pressure campaign on Ukraine. But when he testifies before the House Intelligence Committee on Wednesday, he will have to answer for several inconsistencies that have emerged in his story so far.

headline.main: Why Discrepancies in Gordon Sondland’s Testimony in the Impeachment Inquiry Loom Large
